Posts.EditableText:
For the inventory, use the `ScopeInventory`function. For the room, `ScopeVisibleNotHeld`. You may find `FilterByAttribute` and `FilterByType` useful too, so you get just get the objects you want from the list (just weapons or just monsters). Then there is `PickOneObject ` to randomly pick one object from the list.
```
// get all objects in room
l = ScopeVisibleNotHeld()
// filter out anything not of the monster type
l = FilterByType(l, "monster")
// pick one at random
foe = PickOneObject (l)
